# REFERENCE ONLY — secrets now live in the SharedClaude `secrets` table, NOT on
# the NAS and NOT in a file. db/schema.sql already seeds every key below; set the
# real values with:   uv run plugins/core/scripts/kb.py secret-set <KEY> '<value>' --service <svc>
# This file is kept only as a human-readable map of which keys exist and where
# each value comes from (see the original assistant/integrations/*.md docs).

